org.apache.juneau.msgpack

Class MsgPackSerializerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.Context
      • org.apache.juneau.serializer.SerializerContext
        • org.apache.juneau.msgpack.MsgPackSerializerContext

  • public final class MsgPackSerializerContext
extends SerializerContext
    Configurable properties on the MsgPackSerializer class.

    Context properties are set by calling ContextFactory.setProperty(String, Object) on the context factory returned CoreApi.getContextFactory().

    The following convenience methods are also provided for setting context properties:

    • MsgPackSerializer.setProperty(String,Object)
    • MsgPackSerializer.setProperties(ObjectMap)
    • MsgPackSerializer.addNotBeanClasses(Class[])
    • MsgPackSerializer.addBeanFilters(Class[])
    • MsgPackSerializer.addPojoSwaps(Class[])
    • MsgPackSerializer.addToDictionary(Class[])
    • MsgPackSerializer.addImplClass(Class,Class)

    See ContextFactory for more information about context properties.

    Configurable properties on the MessagePack serializer

    None.

    Configurable properties inherited from parent classes
    • BeanContext - Properties associated with handling beans on serializers and parsers.
      • SerializerContext - Configurable properties common to all serializers.
